Founded in 1990, Lightweight have over 20 years of 🇩🇪  German 🇩🇪Engineering expertise. Ex pro cyclist Dan Lloyd has the pleasure of unboxing the Lightweight Meilenstein carbon clinchers.   

In this unboxing, we also have the kit including;
SwissStop brake pads
Quick release skewers
Valve extenders, tyre Levers, pump adaptors and grease
Cleaning kit
